page.title: 02My Family by Stuart.
page.content: Vicky is 130cm she is large for her age and she likes collecting rubbers. She is not the type of girl who likes sports. she wears summer clothes in the winter. MARTIN is 142cm tall. He likes playing football and rounders. He likes computers and complicated games. STUART <my self> is 133cm small but he is good at football. He likes swimming but but doesn't like compicated games. He likes easy games. JEOFF (my dad)is tall and he likes football,table-tennis and cricket. He likes wearing shorts. In his spare time he cleans our swimming pool and goes rifle shooting in the garden. Jenny (my mum)is not very sporty. She likes "Songs of Praise" and collects antiques." Songs of Praise" is a programme of hymns sung in a church.
